snippet.title: Mimics - the game you play with your face, out now on iOS & Android! - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it for iOS here:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mimics/id1037354797?l=de&ls=1&mt=8
Get it for Android here:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.navel.faceitdis

Here comes the game that you play with your face!
Mimics is a hilarious online and local multiplayer game about imitating faces with your friends and family. Given a picture, you mimic the facial expression and watch your friends try and guess which picture you portrayed.

Facebook
https://www.facebook.com/MimicsTheGame/
